<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>命令行 on Luca's Blog</title><link>https://wlj.me/tags/%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C/</link><description>Recent content in 命令行 on Luca's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://wlj.me/tags/%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>npm install -g @google/gemini-cli</title><link>https://wlj.me/posts/2241270/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wlj.me/posts/2241270/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Homebrew 的更新过程太慢了，而且 gemini-cli 总是弹出升级提示，很烦。于是决定卸载它：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;brew uninstall gemini-cli
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;改用 npm 来管理：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g @google/gemini-cli
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description></item><item><title>用 mdp 在命令行下做 markdown 的 slide show</title><link>https://wlj.me/posts/yong-mdp-zai-ming-ling-xing-xia-zuo-markdown-de-slide-show/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wlj.me/posts/yong-mdp-zai-ming-ling-xing-xia-zuo-markdown-de-slide-show/</guid><description>&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;brew install mdp
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>